# Frontend DOM Patterns

## Vanilla TS Only
- document.createElement, appendChild, classList
- No React, Vue, Svelte, or JSX

## Panel Registration
```typescript
import { registerPanel } from './panel-manager';
registerPanel({ id, title, badge, init: buildBody });
```

## Event Subscription
```typescript
window.addEventListener('portfolio-updated', (e) => {
  const snapshot = (e as CustomEvent).detail;
  // update UI
});
```

## Styling
- CSS variables: --bg-panel, --text-accent, --sentiment-positive
- Classes: .profit (green), .loss (red)
- No Tailwind, no CSS-in-JS
